    • Method Detail

      • scrub

        public static boolean scrub(@Nullable
                            android.content.Intent intent)
        Scrubs an Intent for bad extras in Intent.getExtras().

        Note: this method does not recursively scrub Bundles that may be within the extras Bundle.

        Parameters:
        intent - Intent whose extras will be scrubbed. If intent has at least one bad extra, the extra Bundle will be cleared. Note that intent may be mutated by this method.
        Returns:
        true if intent's extras were cleared, false if intent was not mutated.

      • scrub

        public static boolean scrub(@Nullable
                            android.os.Bundle bundle)
        Scrubs a Bundle for bad extras.

        Note: this method does not recursively scrub Bundles that may be within bundle.

        Parameters:
        bundle - Bundle whose extras will be scrubbed. If bundle has at least one bad extra, the Bundle will be cleared. Note that bundle may be mutated by this method.
        Returns:
        true if bundle was cleared, false if bundle was not mutated.
